{"tid":893240,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【龍市二期🐲 】荃灣中心細戶跌至405萬沽 樓上單位4月造價要440萬","createTime":"2018-11-07T12:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T17:22:13.000Z","uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"95e0a02c55dff075c44310a4e4a5c2de37b685d0","tid":893240,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"荃灣上車屋苑荃灣中心細單位再跌價，剛以405萬易手，快跌穿400萬水平，隨時重回九成樓按之列。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業首席高級營業經理鍾家豪指，屋苑6座低層H室，實用面積324平方呎，內籠欠裝修，業主早於上月放盤，叫價510萬元，最終以405萬元易手，減價105萬或20.6%，呎價1.25萬。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，是次成交的樓上單位今年4月以440萬元易手，今次成交價還要低35萬或8%。鍾家豪指，屋苑6座中高層面積一樣的E室單位，方向一樣，8月份高位見525萬元，形容高位跌價22.9%。"},{"pid":"8e59ed37026a93a2e180ef1f070a45ef0fac3dc4","tid":893240,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"525萬個位呎價要1.6萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但荃灣中心都幾舊下"},{"pid":"b6b3c3708560ab6e3f30aad0639141e2dc9b2c95","tid":893240,"uid":37599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e59ed37026a93a2e180ef1f070a45ef0fac3dc4","tid":893240,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"525萬個位呎價要1.6萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但荃灣中心都幾舊下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"根本就係廢西樓，300萬都唔值，唔知點解五百幾萬仲有人接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368d60222acb37c6f3b34ee3d462e71118e9bb00","tid":893240,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T14:03:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddc3c669af782fe238736e887a769a4c84705388","tid":893240,"uid":35941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6b3c3708560ab6e3f30aad0639141e2dc9b2c95","tid":893240,"uid":37599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e59ed37026a93a2e180ef1f070a45ef0fac3dc4","tid":893240,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T1